<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if self-test was successful.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE if self-test failed.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None.</para></simplesect>
